Part 1 of assignment 2 for CSE-545 Software Security
===================================================

Author : Vignesh Jayabalan (1207606773/SacredSaga)

File description :
	1) Makefile - to make the shell script executable
	2) secret_sender - shell script to run the python
					   script
	3) secret.py - The core python file that contains 
				   the complete implementation as
				   described below

Description : 

	1) read the parametes from command line and parse 
	it into the correct variables.
	2) depending on the type create the packets using 
	the scapy package functionalities.
	3) set the destination IP, fragment offset and id
	4) send the packets.